'''Imperial Forensic Intelligence''' was a suborganization of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. After the destruction of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]], [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] [[Izbela Saarrj]] reported of a new threat under the name of [[Tyber Zann]].

